result.name: ipo-prompt
result.notes: In line with Government guidelines issued at the beginning of 2009, the Intellectual Property Office is required to pay 80% of all It's undisputed supplier Invoices within 5 days of receipt. This is to ensure good practice and cash flow is kept between us and our suppliers.
